Enum Transform

    • java.lang.Enum<Transform>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Transform>
    public enum Transform
extends java.lang.Enum<Transform>
    This class can be used to get all the possible transformation on the board and therefore to get all the symmetries of the board.
    Author:
    Bram Pulles
